# Sauce Demo Functional Test Cases

This document outlines the structured test cases designed to validate the core inventory, product routing, and checkout functionalities of the Sauce Demo e-commerce platform. 

---

## 📊 Requirement Traceability Matrix (RTM)

The matrix below maps business requirements to their corresponding test cases and links them directly to discovered defects from the `BUG_REPORT_LOG.md`.

| Requirement ID | Requirement Description | Test Case ID | Test Case Summary | Status | Linked Bug |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **REQ-INV-01** | Inventory images must dynamically match the listed product details. | `TC-INV-001` | Verify inventory product images match product descriptions. | ❌ **FAILED** | Bug #1: All product images are broken |
| **REQ-RT-02** | Clicking a product must route the user to its specific detail page. | `TC-RT-002` | Verify product page routing and price accuracy. | ❌ **FAILED** | Bug #2: Product opens a broken page |
| **REQ-CHK-03**| Checkout form must validate inputs and proceed to the review page. | `TC-CHK-003` | Verify checkout form entry and validation flow. | ❌ **FAILED** | Bug #3: Form doesn't allow user to complete order |

