## 📝 Detailed Test Cases

### 🛠️ Inventory Module

#### **Test Case ID:** `TC-INV-001`
* **Description:** Verify that all product images on the inventory page load correctly and correspond to their listed items (e.g., Backpack, Fleece Jacket).
* **Pre-conditions:** User is on the Swag Labs login page.
* **Test Data:** URL: `https://www.saucedemo.com/`, Credentials: `problem_user`

| Step # | Test Steps | Expected Result | Actual Result | Status |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| 1 | Navigate to saucedemo.com. | Login page loads successfully. | As expected. | PASS |
| 2 | Enter valid credentials and click "Login". | User is authenticated and redirected to the inventory catalog page (`/inventory.html`). | As expected. | PASS |
| 3 | Inspect the product images for all items listed in the catalog. | Every item displays a high-resolution, unique image matching its product title. | All items display an identical placeholder picture of a dog. Console shows network failures. | **FAIL** |

---

### 🔄 Routing Module

#### **Test Case ID:** `TC-RT-002`
* **Description:** Verify that clicking on an individual product name successfully routes the user to that specific product's details view with the correct pricing.
* **Pre-conditions:** User is logged into the inventory page.
* **Test Data:** Target Item: "Sauce Labs Fleece Jacket"

| Step # | Test Steps | Expected Result | Actual Result | Status |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| 1 | Locate the "Sauce Labs Fleece Jacket" on the inventory page. | Product name link is visible and clickable. | As expected. | PASS |
| 2 | Click on the product name text link. | User is routed to the individual item page (`/inventory-item.html`) displaying description and correct price ($49.99). | Page displays "ITEM NOT FOUND" and price displays as a broken math formula (-1). | **FAIL** |

---

### 🛒 Checkout Module

#### **Test Case ID:** `TC-CHK-003`
* **Description:** Verify that the "Checkout: Your Information" form accepts alphanumeric characters, retains user input across fields, and navigates forward upon valid submission.
* **Pre-conditions:** User has added at least one item to the cart and navigated to the checkout step (`/checkout-step-one.html`).
* **Test Data:** First Name: `John`, Last Name: `Doe`, Zip Code: `12345`

| Step # | Test Steps | Expected Result | Actual Result | Status |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| 1 | Click into the "First Name" field and type "John". | Field accepts input and displays "John". | As expected. | PASS |
| 2 | Click into the "Last Name" field and type "Doe". | Field accepts input. Prior fields retain their data. | Inputting text into Last Name instantly clears the First Name field. Fields only accept single characters. | **FAIL** |
| 3 | Complete remaining fields and click the "Continue" button. | Input data is stored, and user proceeds to checkout step two (`/checkout-step-two.html`). | Form resets completely, displays a false validation error: "Error: Last Name is required." | **FAIL** |
